## 📁 Project Structure

```
CivicConnect/
├── README.md
├── Backend/
│   ├── server.js
│   ├── .env.example
│   ├── config/db.js
│   ├── models/
│   │   ├── User.js          # role, adminLevel (0-3), ward, district, city
│   │   └── Issue.js         # category, status, priority, currentLevel,
│   │                        #   upvotes, escalationHistory[], comments[]
