## 🌐 Environment Variables

### `Backend/.env`
```env
PORT=5000
NODE_ENV=development
MONGO_URI=mongodb+srv://...
JWT_SECRET=your_secret_min_32_chars
JWT_EXPIRES_IN=7d
CLIENT_URL=http://localhost:5173
ESCALATE_L1_HOURS=48
ESCALATE_L2_HOURS=72
ESCALATION_CRON_MINUTES=60
```

### `Frontend/.env`
```env
# Development — Vite proxy handles routing, relative URL works everywhere
VITE_API_URL=/api

# Production — set this in the Vercel dashboard instead of committing it
# VITE_API_URL=https://civic-connect-4w0n.onrender.com/api
```

